	6. if list1[i]>list2[j], add list1[i] to the result and iterate i.
	7. if list1[i]<list2[j], add list2[j] to the result and iterate j.
	8. if they are equal, find in which list, greater number pops up earlier. if it happens in list1, add list1[i] to result and increment i else add list2[j] and increment j.

